agement之類有用資料<br />\n等大家客觀知道同溫層之外咩反應<br />\n就算我哋唔做嘅話<br />\n對家都可能會做(記得雨傘後撐警定周融之類好似都做有過)<br />\n如果可以爭取時間做多幾款copy做長d時間更好<br />\n<br />\n有咩幫手請出聲<br />\nP牌仔都可以略盡綿力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b775c9f5b86267526c6338fba821c0b641c923","tid":1277194,"uid":53463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:09:09.000Z","msg":"喺九巴同城新app都見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e84c84c655b2470c7ca2a3ecd2ea5ae0cd26146","tid":1277194,"uid":213384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13b775c9f5b86267526c6338fba821c0b641c923","tid":1277194,"uid":53463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:09:09.000Z","msg":"喺九巴同城新app都見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:09:54.000Z","msg":"如果大家見到隻AD, 不防SCREEN CAP出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67025e1f41bb8dbc84b693663ae9252c64cc553f","tid":1277194,"uid":166117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bb02889ae75f79da88e0248c35019f5cdee7dc6","tid":1277194,"uid":213384,"like":139,"dislike":1,"score":138,"citedBy":14,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:26:12.000Z","msg":"大家好...<br />\n呢幾隻GOOGLE AD係我同幾個人夾錢搞出黎<br />\nD相, 同字都得到左當時人同意先用<br />\n<br />\n錢唔算多, 未必出到幾多日<br />\n我地呢幾個人...未必敢衝...但都想出一分力<br />\n<br />\n希望見到AD既義士, 覺得有人支持<br />\n希望見到AD既中產, 唔好blame行得前既人<br />\n希望見到AD既父母, 試下了解一下青年人<br />\n<br />\n如果大家覺得D隻稿唔靚....唔好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S.大家見到可以盡情CLICK, 因為唔係pay per clic